<emphasis box="[1076,1249,1941,1966]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="168">campo rupestre</emphasis>
and grasslands.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[136,1452,1220,2003]" box="[189,1273,1976,2003]" pageId="1" pageNumber="168">
